(4, 'Portable Backyard BBQ', 'Glass', '1554606214Portable-Backyard-BBQ.jpg', '2500', '4500', '0', '<p><strong>Product Description</strong><br />\r\nSteel Portable Charcoal Barbeque BBQ Grill<br />\r\nCover with adjustable vent Carry handles Retractable metal legs<br />\r\nBrand New Steel Portable Charcoal Barbeque BBQ Grill<br />\r\nConstructed of high heat resistant stainless steel. This stainless steel barbecue grill is portable use at ground level or table top. The indoor barbecue grill has cooking surface with a nonstick coating for searing foods just like on an outdoor grill. Non-stick surface provides easy clean-up. Open grilling surface allows for a smokey, barbecue flavor. The charcoal barbecue grill is a simple and delicious way to get the backyard grilling experience anywhere you choose.<br />\r\nQuick Details<br />\r\nProduct Size 48x30x26cm<br />\r\nGrill Size 41&times;26.5cm<br />\r\n<br />\r\n<strong>Specifications</strong><br />\r\nNon-stick surface provides easy clean-up. Prepare delicious grilled, bake and fry foods on this combination stainless steel barbecue grill device. Prepare fish to perfection and prevent it from falling into your grill. This is how to get a party rolling. This stainless steel barbecue grill is perfect for tailgating, camping, fishing or just cooking on the patio. This stainless steel barbecue grill is portable use at ground level or table top. Simple non-stick fish grill basket with a wooden handle so avoid hand scalding. This basket makes barbecuing your catch-of-the-day neat and easy. The charcoal barbecue grill is a simple and delicious way to get the backyard grilling experience anywhere you choose. Enjoy the great taste of food cooked on the grill all year long with this indoor barbecue grill</p>', '2018-01-31T01:01', 'korea', '', 'In Stock', '', 'within 3 days', '73', '2', '2018-12-29 08:13:01', '2019-06-21 03:21:23'),
