the day. Maintenance stage: Take 2 scoops of Cell-Tech with 12 oz of water immediately following your workout. If you&#39;re not training that day, take 2 scoops with 12 oz of water in the morning when you wake up.</p>', '0', '0', '0', '0', NULL, '0', '2019-04-04 20:12:00', '2019-05-23 14:59:55'),
